quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  67,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  67,1,woh ( khuda ) jis ke haath mein badshahi hai barri barket wala hai. aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  67,2,isi ne mout aur zindagi ko pedakiya taakay tumhari azmaish kere ke tum mein kon achay amal karta hai. aur woh zabardast ( aur ) bakhsnay wala hai
  67,3,is ne saat aasman oopar taley banaye. ( ae dekhnay walay )kiya to ( khuda ) rehman ki aafrinash mein kuch nuqs daikhta hai? zara aankhh utha kar dekh bhala tujh ko ( aasman mein ) koi shagaaf nazar aata hai ?
  67,4,"phir do baara ( sah baara ) nazar kar, to nazar ( har baar ) tairay paas nakaam aur thak kar lout aeye gi"
  67,5,aur hum ne qareeb ke aasman ko ( taron ke ) charaghoon se zeenat di. aur un ko shetan ke maarny ka aala banaya aur un ke liye dehakti aag ka azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  67,6,aur jin logon ne apne perwar-digaar se inkaarkiya un ke liye jahannum ka azaab hai. aur woh bura thikana hai
  67,7,jab woh is mein daaley jayen ge to is ka cheekhna chalana sunen ge aur woh josh maar rahi hogi
  67,8,goya maaray josh ke phatt parre gi. jab is mein un ki koi jamaat daali jaye gi to dozakh ke Darogha un se poucheen ge ke tumahray paas koi hadaayat karne wala nahi aaya tha ?
  67,9,woh kahin ge kyun nahi zaroor hadaayat karne wala aaya tha lekin hum ne is ko jhutla diya aur kaha ke khuda ne to koi cheez nazil hi nahi ki. tum to barri ghalti mein ( parre hue ) ho
  67,10,aur kahin ge agar hum suntay ya samajte hotay to dozokhiyo+A5362 mein nah hotay
  67,11,pas woh apne gunah ka iqraar karlen ge. so dozakhiyon ke liye ( rehmat khuda se ) daur hi hai
  67,12,( aur ) jo log ban dekhe apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain un ke liye bakhshish aur ajar azeem hai
  67,13,aur tum ( log ) baat posheeda kaho ya zahir. woh dil ke bheidoon taq se waaqif hai
  67,14,bhala jis ne pedakiya woh be khabar hai? woh to posheeda baton ka jan-nay wala aur ( har cheez se ) aagah hai
  67,15,wohi to hai jis ne tumahray liye zameen ko naramkiya to is ki raahon mein chalo phiro aur khuda ka ( diya ho ) rizaq khao aur tum ko isi ke paas ( qabron se ) nikal kar jana hai
  67,16,kiya tum is se jo aasman mein hai be khauf ho ke tum ko zameen mein dhansa day aur woh is waqt harkat karne lagey
  67,17,kiya tum is se jo aasman mein hai nidar ho ke tum par kanker bhari howa chore day. so tum anqareeb jaan lau ge ke mera darana kaisa hai
  67,18,aur jo log un se pehlay they unhon ne bhi jhatlaya tha so ( dekh lau ke ) mera kaisa azaab howa
  67,19,kiya unhon ne apne suron par urrtay hue janwaron ko nahi dekha jo paron ko phelaaye rehtay hain aur un ko sukairh bhi letay hain. khuda ke siwa inhen koi thaam nahi sakta. be shak woh har cheez ko dekh raha hai
  67,20,bhala aisa kon hai jo tumhari fouj ho kar khuda ke siwa tumhari madad kar sakay. kafir to dhokay mein hain
  67,21,bhala agar woh apna rizaq band karle to kon hai jo tum ko rizaq day? lekin yeh sar kashi aur nafrat mein phansay hue hain
  67,22,bhala jo shakhs chalta howa munh ke bil gir parta hai woh seedhay raste par hai ya woh jo seedhay raste par barabar chal raha ho ?
  67,23,kaho woh khuda hi to hai jis ne tum ko pedakiya. aur tumahray kaan aur ankhen aur dil banaye ( magar ) tum kam ahsaan mantay ho
  67,24,keh do ke wohi hai jis ne tum ko zameen mein phelaya aur isi ke rubaroo tum jama kiye jao ge
  67,25,aur kafir kehte hain ke agar tum sachey ho to yeh vayd kab ( poora ) hoga ?
  67,26,keh do is ka ilm khuda hi ko hai. aur mein to khol khol kar dar sunanay dainay wala hon
  67,27,so jab woh dekh len ge ke woh ( wada ) qareeb agaya to kafiroon ke munh buray ho jaien ge aur ( un se ) kaha jaye ga ke yeh wohi hai jis ke tum khawastgah they
  67,28,kaho ke bhala dekho to agar khuda mujh ko aur mere sathiyon ko halaak kardey ya hum par meharbani kere. to kon hai kafiroon ko dukh dainay walay azaab se panah day ?
  67,29,keh do ke woh jo ( khuday-e ) rehman ( hai ) hum isi par imaan laaye aur isi par bhrosa rakhtay hain. tum ko jald maloom hojaye ga ke Sarih gumraahi mein kon par raha tha
  67,30,kaho ke bhala dekho to agar tumhara pani ( jo tum peetay ho aur bartay ho ) khushk hojaye to ( khuda ke ) siwa kon hai jo tumahray liye sheree pani ka chashma baha laaye
